Singapore is still in the circuit breaker period but something to be grateful for is that our postmans are still helping us deliver letters🙆🏻‍♀️ taking this period to drop traditional letters to our love ones who are also confined to their homes 😘 >>swipe right to see process video!

ours shut down all international ins and outs for months now! 😭

gosh i haven't sent you a letter in so long i really need to get back to it :'))
